data.description: This massive property is waiting for a large family to make it a home, with all the bells and whistles at your fingertips. This home features 5 bedrooms 2.5 baths, an open family room to the kitchen, and a formal living room/dining room. A huge loft upstairs to keep the kiddos entertained. The master suite is massive with a huge walk-in closet to match, and a jetted tub to soak in after a long day at work. Plus a big backyard to watch the kids play. (the owner is offering a $1,500 painting allowance with the right offer.)
